		{
			description: [
				"Welcome to &bCobblemon&r — Pokémon as Minecraft was always meant to experience them."
				""
				"Unlike traditional Pokémon games, Cobblemon creatures live in the open world alongside everything else. They spawn in biomes that suit them, react to the environment, and exist whether you engage them or not."
				""
				"Start simple: find a wild Cobblemon and get close. You don't need to battle it. Just observe."
				""
				"&7Tip: Cobblemon are more active at dusk — try exploring near dusk for Normal-types.&r"
			]
			icon: "cobblemon:poke_ball"
			id: "1000000000000005"
			min_width: 320
			rewards: [
