		{
			dependencies: ["1000000000000005"]
			description: [
				"Time to make your first catch."
				""
				"Throw a Poké Ball at a wild Cobblemon to start the catch attempt. The lower their HP, the better your odds — weaken them in battle first, then throw."
				""
				"A few things to know:"
				"• &ePoké Balls&r are your basic catch tool — craft them from Apricorns"
				"• Different balls have different catch rates and specialties"
				"• The first Cobblemon you catch becomes your starter — choose wisely"
				""
				"&7Tip: Lower HP dramatically increases catch rate. Weaken before throwing.&r"
			]
			id: "1000000000000009"
			min_width: 330
			rewards: [
				{
					count: 10
