		}
		{
			dependencies: ["1000000000000009"]
			description: [
				"Give your Cobblemon a name. It's a small thing, but it matters."
				""
				"After catching, a naming screen will appear. You can name it anything you like, or leave it with its species name. A named Cobblemon feels different — it's yours."
				""
				"You can rename any Cobblemon later by interacting with it and opening its summary screen."
				""
				"&7Tip: Nicknames don't affect stats, but they do make your bond feel real.&r"
			]
			id: "100000000000000C"
			min_width: 300
			rewards: [{
