		{
			dependencies: ["1000000000000010"]
			description: [
				"The &ePokédex&r is your field guide to every Cobblemon species. Open it from your inventory and look up any species you've encountered — it logs entry data automatically when you see or catch a Cobblemon."
				""
				"Each entry shows:"
				"• Type and weaknesses"
				"• Spawn biomes and conditions"
				"• Evolution methods and requirements"
				"• Base stats and move pool"
				""
				"Look up 5 entries to get familiar with how it works. You'll be using it constantly."
				""
				"&7Tip: You don't need to catch them — simply encountering a Cobblemon logs an entry.&r"
			]
