		{
			dependencies: ["1000000000000014"]
			description: [
				"Ten entries in the Pokédex means ten different species encountered. That's a real start — but the world holds hundreds more."
				""
				"Every biome has its own Cobblemon population. Forests, oceans, mountains, caves, and even modded dimensions all have unique spawns you won't find anywhere else."
				""
				"Exploration is the engine of progress in Cobblemon. The more ground you cover, the more species you'll find."
				""
				"&7Tip: Explore multiple biomes — each has entirely unique Cobblemon populations.&r"
			]
