			description: [
				"The &eCobblemon Spawn Notification&r mod alerts you when a rare Cobblemon appears nearby. Keep an eye on your screen — these windows don't stay open long."
				""
				"Rare Cobblemon are significantly harder to find than common species. They may spawn only under specific conditions — time of day, weather, biome, or pure chance."
				""
				"When the notification fires, drop what you're doing and go. Rare spawns don't wait."
				""
				"&7Tip: Stay alert even when you're doing other things — rare notifications can appear at any time.&r"
